national pizza <piza> corrects figure
    pittsburg, kan., march 16 - 
national pizza co said the seven straw hat piza restaurants in los
angeles and bakersfield, calif., that it announced plans to buy friday
are expected to generate annual sales of about 3,800,000 dlrs, not the
eight mln dlrs the company originally announced. the company said it
will convert the restaurants to pizza hut units. closing is expected
around march 31. reuter 
